WEBVTT

01:25.710 --> 01:34.930
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.280 --> 01:37.920
[Episode 27]

01:38.220 --> 01:41.710
[Wenzhou Bus Station]

01:41.710 --> 01:44.670
[Dangerous items
strictly prohibited on board.]

01:45.680 --> 01:47.479
What are you looking around for?

01:47.700 --> 01:48.810
Nothing.

01:49.400 --> 01:50.340
Looking for love, huh?

01:50.340 --> 01:51.150
No!

01:52.640 --> 01:53.170
Have one.

01:53.320 --> 01:53.979
No, thanks.

01:54.110 --> 01:55.870
Let's go. Let's eat it on the bus.

01:55.870 --> 01:56.400
Let's go.

01:57.370 --> 01:57.900
Careful.

02:02.200 --> 02:03.930
How are things with Chief Engineer Pan?

02:03.930 --> 02:05.060
Chief Engineer Pan?

02:06.000 --> 02:06.760
I have to

02:06.760 --> 02:08.020
get him on board no matter what!

02:08.020 --> 02:08.750
At least I can

02:08.759 --> 02:10.240
finally get even with Director Wang.

02:10.240 --> 02:10.590
Okay.

02:10.750 --> 02:12.090
Once things are settled here,

02:12.090 --> 02:13.550
we need to hurry to Russia.

02:13.810 --> 02:14.960
The weather gets cold quickly there.

02:14.960 --> 02:17.760
We'll miss the season
if we don't rush production.

02:18.079 --> 02:19.020
Like I don't know that.

02:19.020 --> 02:19.710
I've been to Russia

02:19.710 --> 02:20.840
more times than you.

02:24.010 --> 02:24.670
[Wenzhou; Jinhua]

02:24.670 --> 02:25.680
[Wenzhou; Shaoxing]

02:30.260 --> 02:31.100
Xu Shengli!

02:42.300 --> 02:44.730
[Dangerous items
strictly prohibited on board.]

02:43.870 --> 02:44.800
Why are you here?

02:45.329 --> 02:46.070
What?

02:46.380 --> 02:48.110
You came to see me off in person?

02:48.680 --> 02:49.540
Not funny, huh?

02:50.210 --> 02:51.020
You guys talk.

02:52.690 --> 02:53.350
Wait, wait.

02:54.280 --> 02:54.960
It's fine. You don't have to!

02:54.960 --> 02:55.920
Come on, let me!

02:56.100 --> 02:56.560
Come on.

02:59.100 --> 03:00.230
Did Mr. Ye help us out

03:00.360 --> 03:01.660
with the factory?

03:01.800 --> 03:03.130
Please thank him for us.

03:03.850 --> 03:05.180
Good that he could help.

03:08.000 --> 03:09.930
My mom insisted I bring this to you.

03:09.930 --> 03:10.860
Eat it on the way.

03:11.660 --> 03:12.940
Okay. Tell your mom

03:12.970 --> 03:15.030
I'll come visit her again next month.

03:15.070 --> 03:15.800
Alright.

03:16.130 --> 03:17.390
No need to be so polite.

03:20.660 --> 03:27.610
[Dangerous items
strictly prohibited on board.]

03:23.540 --> 03:24.740
Be careful. Careful.

03:28.960 --> 03:30.520
Then take care of your mom,

03:30.550 --> 03:32.250
and take good care of yourself as well.

03:32.250 --> 03:33.100
If you fall ill,

03:33.100 --> 03:34.430
no one will take care of her,

03:34.430 --> 03:36.160
and no one will take care of you.

03:40.210 --> 03:41.329
All right. Go now.

03:44.060 --> 03:45.410
Be safe on the road.

03:49.170 --> 03:52.170
Don't go sticking your neck out
if something happens.

03:53.220 --> 03:54.750
Okay, I'll go then.

03:59.870 --> 04:00.370
Bye.

04:04.530 --> 04:05.100
Bye.

04:17.140 --> 04:17.579
Bye.

04:49.440 --> 04:50.450
If you really can't bear to leave,

04:50.450 --> 04:51.070
just stay.

04:51.430 --> 04:52.840
I can manage the business on my own.

04:52.840 --> 04:54.330
I'll still give you your share.

04:54.330 --> 04:54.870
No need!

04:56.659 --> 04:57.659
Let's make money!

05:11.010 --> 05:13.470
Ivan really has built up
quite an operation.

05:13.870 --> 05:14.830
No wonder people say

05:14.830 --> 05:15.500
that the best leather jackets

05:15.500 --> 05:16.890
and shoes on the market

05:16.920 --> 05:18.060
all use his hides.

05:20.840 --> 05:22.070
But we don't know

05:22.130 --> 05:23.130
the trade jargon in Russian.

05:23.130 --> 05:24.360
How are we supposed to communicate?

05:24.360 --> 05:25.300
It doesn't matter.

05:25.300 --> 05:26.630
You only need two things

05:26.660 --> 05:27.310
to do business in Russia:

05:27.310 --> 05:28.840
first, bring a calculator.

05:29.010 --> 05:29.640
Second,

05:29.810 --> 05:30.950
say "Harasho" (very good) to everyone.

05:30.950 --> 05:32.080
Guaranteed to work.

05:32.430 --> 05:33.150
That's him?

05:33.430 --> 05:34.960
-That should be him.
-Ivan!

05:35.150 --> 05:35.580
Yes.

05:36.250 --> 05:37.540
Harasho! Harasho!

05:37.870 --> 05:38.870
You're here.

05:39.990 --> 05:41.330
Was it cold on the way?

05:43.100 --> 05:44.920
Well, we came by train.

05:45.810 --> 05:47.630
There was heating, so it was very warm.

05:47.630 --> 05:48.800
Nice to meet you.

05:48.820 --> 05:49.510
Nice to meet you.

05:49.510 --> 05:50.440
Nice to meet you.

05:50.570 --> 05:52.570
You speak really good Chinese.

05:52.830 --> 05:54.430
When friends come from afar,

05:54.690 --> 05:56.350
you must show them sincerity.

05:57.830 --> 05:59.830
He even knows our Chinese proverbs.

05:59.830 --> 06:01.990
Well, we'd like to see the goods first.

06:02.980 --> 06:04.200
Take a look at the hides.

06:04.200 --> 06:04.690
Sure.

06:05.830 --> 06:06.270
Okay.

06:21.270 --> 06:22.560
They could've just put it there directly.

06:22.560 --> 06:23.820
Totally unnecessary.

06:52.159 --> 06:53.690
They're top-grain leather

06:53.790 --> 06:55.000
from Chita's ranches.

06:55.000 --> 06:56.940
See how firmly frozen they are.

06:59.800 --> 07:01.730
Evenly salted, with no hard spots.

07:01.770 --> 07:02.500
Pretty good.

07:02.630 --> 07:04.470
Very good. Harasho.

07:04.570 --> 07:05.700
You know your stuff.

07:06.920 --> 07:08.050
This batch of goods—

07:08.070 --> 07:10.180
small orders, $4 a piece.

07:10.870 --> 07:13.540
Large orders, $3 per piece.

07:13.890 --> 07:14.750
Three dollars?

07:15.130 --> 07:16.630
In cash, $2.50 a piece.

07:17.800 --> 07:19.950
Look at these buffalo hides.

07:21.390 --> 07:22.740
The quality is excellent.

07:22.740 --> 07:25.630
Perfect for making protective work gloves.

07:26.430 --> 07:28.360
He says these are buffalo hides,

07:28.400 --> 07:29.660
known for durability.

07:31.510 --> 07:32.330
But we don't have

07:32.330 --> 07:33.790
that much money right now.

07:34.659 --> 07:36.390
And the prices are pretty high.

07:37.540 --> 07:40.040
We need 200 pieces of this kind of hide

07:40.580 --> 07:41.840
and 100 buffalo hides.

07:42.970 --> 07:43.900
No problem.

07:44.750 --> 07:47.520
You've already found a factory in China?

07:47.650 --> 07:48.450
Yes, we have.

07:49.040 --> 07:50.010
I-In Wenzhou.

07:50.120 --> 07:51.210
It's fully equipped.

07:51.210 --> 07:51.960
Wenzhou.

07:53.030 --> 07:54.360
I know Wenzhou.

07:54.390 --> 07:55.320
I've been there.

07:56.500 --> 07:58.510
The factories there are really good.

07:58.510 --> 08:00.890
They specialize in leather production.

08:01.440 --> 08:04.650
We Russians also purchase from there.

08:06.250 --> 08:08.060
All I caught was "harasho."

08:08.480 --> 08:10.120
Um... I didn't understand.

08:10.120 --> 08:12.850
Could you just speak simple Chinese?

08:14.950 --> 08:17.210
Get the money ready and pick up the goods.

08:19.770 --> 08:20.130
Okay.

08:22.100 --> 08:22.900
No problem.

08:23.480 --> 08:24.540
To our friendship!

08:24.690 --> 08:25.220
Harasho!

08:26.180 --> 08:26.900
Harasho!

08:28.630 --> 08:29.750
Take care.

08:37.130 --> 08:38.820
The factory deposit is 30,000,

08:38.820 --> 08:40.669
and the hides alone will cost 10,000.

08:40.669 --> 08:41.270
We don't have

08:41.270 --> 08:42.730
that much money right now.

08:43.130 --> 08:44.770
How about we make a couple of trips

08:44.770 --> 08:45.940
to sell some small goods

08:45.940 --> 08:47.410
and raise some startup capital?

08:47.410 --> 08:48.480
If we do that,

08:48.500 --> 08:50.370
how long will it take to get the money?

08:50.370 --> 08:51.340
You just don't know

08:51.340 --> 08:52.670
what kind of person I am.

08:53.120 --> 08:53.720
I'm...

08:54.410 --> 08:55.480
Plenty of people will lend me money

08:55.480 --> 08:56.280
for business.

08:56.360 --> 08:57.080
Let's not go too far—

08:57.080 --> 08:58.100
take Sophia, for example.

08:58.100 --> 08:58.890
She'll definitely chip in.

08:58.890 --> 08:59.980
But we can't take money from a woman,

08:59.980 --> 09:00.460
right?

09:00.910 --> 09:02.150
Here's the plan—
I'll go back, make some calls,

09:02.150 --> 09:03.200
and ask some friends to lend us some.

09:03.200 --> 09:04.060
Piece of cake!

09:05.100 --> 09:05.560
Well...

09:06.080 --> 09:08.600
When I reach out,
support comes from everywhere!

09:08.600 --> 09:09.250
Okay, okay.

09:09.250 --> 09:10.580
Let's go. Get in the car.

09:10.820 --> 09:12.480
I'll drive, and you sit there.

09:17.910 --> 09:18.570
M-Mr. Duan,

09:19.170 --> 09:20.000
let me tell you.

09:20.000 --> 09:21.410
I, Ma Xiaojun—Lucky Ma—

09:21.440 --> 09:23.170
stay true to my name and myself,

09:23.240 --> 09:23.530
right?

09:23.530 --> 09:24.440
You know what kind of person I am.

09:24.440 --> 09:26.250
We've known each other for so long!

09:26.250 --> 09:26.880
Xiaojun,

09:27.320 --> 09:28.590
of course I know you.

09:28.740 --> 09:29.620
I trust you.

09:30.410 --> 09:31.340
But you also know

09:31.360 --> 09:31.860
my business hasn't been

09:31.860 --> 09:33.660
going well these past few years.

09:34.030 --> 09:35.190
So this time,

09:35.620 --> 09:36.750
I really can't help you.

09:36.750 --> 09:37.310
How about this?

09:37.310 --> 09:39.280
Try asking someone else,

09:39.340 --> 09:39.890
okay?

09:40.270 --> 09:41.270
Alright, then...

09:41.550 --> 09:41.980
Alright.

09:41.980 --> 09:43.530
I'll treat you to a meal when I get back.

09:43.530 --> 09:44.190
Hanging up.

09:44.340 --> 09:45.010
Okay.

09:53.510 --> 09:54.250
Let me guess—

09:55.200 --> 09:57.800
someone calling
to borrow money again, right?

09:58.520 --> 09:59.580
You guessed right.

10:00.750 --> 10:01.410
That was...

10:02.270 --> 10:03.170
a young friend I met

10:03.170 --> 10:04.440
about four or five years ago.

10:04.440 --> 10:05.040
Recently,

10:05.100 --> 10:07.390
he's been doing business
with a group of young people.

10:07.390 --> 10:08.130
But none of them

10:08.130 --> 10:09.130
have proper jobs,

10:09.220 --> 10:10.600
and they even live in
a basement here.

10:10.600 --> 10:12.130
Well, how can I lend them...

10:12.770 --> 10:13.770
Don't look down on

10:13.770 --> 10:15.370
those who live in basements.

10:15.370 --> 10:17.100
Who hasn't lived in one before?

10:20.890 --> 10:21.750
You don't know.

10:22.020 --> 10:22.990
This young man

10:23.020 --> 10:25.120
always jumps from one idea to another.

10:25.120 --> 10:26.200
Not long ago, he took them

10:26.200 --> 10:27.260
on a tour doing gigs.

10:27.260 --> 10:29.130
Well, that was totally unrealistic.

10:29.130 --> 10:29.820
Do gigs?

10:30.890 --> 10:31.890
What kind of gigs?

10:33.550 --> 10:35.130
He was with some

10:35.150 --> 10:37.550
childhood friend who plays the saxophone,

10:37.840 --> 10:39.660
and another one is a...

10:39.680 --> 10:40.540
screenwriter.

10:41.370 --> 10:42.390
He spent ages

10:42.390 --> 10:43.460
pitching their plan to me—

10:43.460 --> 10:44.750
said that in three years,

10:44.750 --> 10:47.660
each of them would make half a million.

10:47.980 --> 10:48.690
You tell me,

10:49.170 --> 10:51.230
does that sound remotely realistic?

10:52.150 --> 10:53.880
How much do they want to borrow?

11:01.680 --> 11:02.360
Mr. Duan.

11:07.100 --> 11:07.850
R-Really?

11:08.220 --> 11:09.780
Yes, it's true.

11:09.810 --> 11:10.600
Xiaojun,

11:10.790 --> 11:11.990
you're really lucky.

11:13.250 --> 11:14.690
A business partner of mine

11:14.690 --> 11:16.620
just transferred some money to me.

11:17.170 --> 11:19.030
You called me at the perfect time.

11:19.270 --> 11:19.800
Alright.

11:20.090 --> 11:21.410
Everyone runs into difficulties sometimes.

11:21.410 --> 11:22.340
First thing tomorrow morning

11:22.340 --> 11:23.800
I'll wire the money to you.

11:23.950 --> 11:25.320
Thank you, Mr. Duan! Thank you!

11:25.320 --> 11:26.000
H-How about this:

11:26.000 --> 11:27.250
I'll write an IOU

11:27.250 --> 11:27.940
and send it to you.

11:27.940 --> 11:29.510
Or I can have my friend in our hometown

11:29.510 --> 11:30.000
write an IOU

11:30.000 --> 11:31.100
to you!

11:31.200 --> 11:31.740
And for interest,

11:31.740 --> 11:32.940
we'll go by the bank rate,

11:32.940 --> 11:33.650
whatever that comes to.

11:33.650 --> 11:34.440
Is that okay, Mr. Duan?

11:34.440 --> 11:35.770
Forget about interest.

11:35.960 --> 11:37.470
Take the money and use it.

11:37.750 --> 11:39.510
Just work hard, make money,

11:39.840 --> 11:40.620
and pay back every last yuan

11:40.620 --> 11:42.050
of the 50,000.

11:42.050 --> 11:43.110
That'll be enough.

11:44.630 --> 11:45.320
Thank you, Mr. Duan.

11:45.320 --> 11:46.050
You're really too kind.

11:46.050 --> 11:46.940
Really, I don't even know

11:46.940 --> 11:47.620
how to thank you.

11:47.620 --> 11:49.290
When I get back, I'll definitely

11:49.290 --> 11:49.720
treat you to a meal.

11:49.720 --> 11:51.420
I'll thank you properly, Mr. Duan.

11:51.420 --> 11:52.950
Alright, don't mention it.

11:53.200 --> 11:53.800
Actually,

11:53.940 --> 11:54.730
this money

11:55.150 --> 11:56.440
isn't exactly

11:56.500 --> 11:57.370
my money.

11:58.150 --> 11:59.370
Alright, let's not talk about this.

11:59.370 --> 11:59.920
Xiaojun,

12:00.130 --> 12:01.530
work hard.

12:01.700 --> 12:03.120
When you've made it

12:03.720 --> 12:04.920
and come back safely,

12:05.120 --> 12:06.270
I'll throw you a welcome party.

12:06.270 --> 12:06.550
Mr. Duan,

12:06.550 --> 12:07.650
when I've made something of myself,
I'll never forget you.

12:07.650 --> 12:08.720
You're like a real brother to me!

12:08.720 --> 12:10.170
When I get back, we'll swear brotherhood,

12:10.170 --> 12:10.700
brother.

12:10.840 --> 12:12.480
Okay, I won't keep you any longer.

12:12.480 --> 12:13.280
Get some rest.

12:20.410 --> 12:23.300
Yes, yes.

12:25.910 --> 12:27.120
Ura!

12:28.250 --> 12:29.050
Come on, Duan.

12:31.170 --> 12:32.430
Promise me something.

12:32.840 --> 12:34.320
No matter what happens in the future,

12:34.320 --> 12:36.720
don't tell him
that this money came from me.

12:37.480 --> 12:37.840
Okay.

12:38.250 --> 12:39.460
You've already said so.

12:39.460 --> 12:40.070
Relax.

12:40.100 --> 12:41.100
I won't say a word.

12:42.620 --> 12:43.480
But...

12:44.510 --> 12:45.840
I'm genuinely puzzled.

12:46.720 --> 12:47.300
Mr. Chu,

12:47.410 --> 12:49.410
you're not even that close.

12:50.630 --> 12:51.690
Why did you do that?

12:57.120 --> 12:57.780
Just right.

12:58.560 --> 12:59.620
Numbers check out.

13:03.100 --> 13:05.070
Here! Count it!

13:05.860 --> 13:07.740
No need. I trust you.

13:08.670 --> 13:10.130
He's quite a stand-up guy.

13:13.080 --> 13:16.550
Yellow cowhide, $10 a piece.

13:16.860 --> 13:18.670
Water buffalo hide, $6.

13:18.870 --> 13:19.820
No, no.

13:19.910 --> 13:21.030
These aren't the prices
we talked about last time.

13:21.030 --> 13:22.460
Why have the prices gone up so many times?

13:22.460 --> 13:24.060
That's how the market works.

13:24.100 --> 13:25.360
If you don't accept it,

13:25.500 --> 13:28.230
that deposit you just gave me
is non-refundable.

13:28.690 --> 13:29.690
What does he mean?

13:29.950 --> 13:31.970
H-He can do business like this?

13:32.220 --> 13:33.600
Are you kidding us?

13:33.820 --> 13:35.200
Look, i-if you do this,

13:35.240 --> 13:36.650
I'll call the police.

13:36.710 --> 13:38.640
We agreed right here the other day.

13:38.750 --> 13:39.960
Uh... the top-grade leather,

13:39.960 --> 13:41.070
$2.50 a piece,

13:41.100 --> 13:42.200
and this kind, $2 a piece.

13:42.200 --> 13:42.910
We did the math

13:42.910 --> 13:44.120
and brought exactly the money.

13:44.120 --> 13:45.450
You can go to the police.

13:46.050 --> 13:47.910
That's just how the market works.

13:48.150 --> 13:49.550
There's nothing I can do.

13:49.600 --> 13:52.510
Bring the rest at 5 PM tomorrow.

14:03.010 --> 14:04.870
You're jacking up the price on us!

14:06.240 --> 14:06.790
Ivan,

14:06.820 --> 14:08.480
do you think we're pushovers?

14:11.690 --> 14:12.710
I'm telling you,

14:13.280 --> 14:15.410
you're not bullying just the two of us.

14:15.670 --> 14:16.200
I'll tell

14:16.230 --> 14:17.370
every single Chinese merchant

14:17.370 --> 14:18.670
to stop doing business with you.

14:18.670 --> 14:19.740
Give us our money back right now.

14:19.740 --> 14:20.270
We're not buying.

14:20.270 --> 14:21.330
Do you understand?

14:27.630 --> 14:29.630
You think a few sticks will scare us?

14:30.460 --> 14:31.460
Kill me then.

14:31.670 --> 14:32.480
-Jun.
-Kill me, come on!

14:32.480 --> 14:33.520
Come on, kill me!

14:35.010 --> 14:36.210
Tomorrow won't work.

14:36.540 --> 14:38.600
We can't get that much money overnight.

14:38.600 --> 14:39.830
Give us two more days.

14:41.820 --> 14:43.480
The day after tomorrow, then.

14:45.940 --> 14:46.930
Wait, where...

14:47.960 --> 14:49.630
Where are we even supposed to
get the money?

14:49.630 --> 14:51.360
Who introduced this guy to you?

14:52.820 --> 14:54.380
That old bastard is truly rotten.

14:54.380 --> 14:55.520
Isn't he just swindling us?

14:55.520 --> 14:57.580
Complaining about it now won't help.

14:57.600 --> 14:59.020
We urgently need this batch of goods.

14:59.020 --> 15:00.900
The factory's all set to start work.

15:00.900 --> 15:02.080
But we don't have enough money.

15:02.080 --> 15:04.010
We put together exactly enough money
based on the original prices.

15:04.010 --> 15:04.890
How much are we short?

15:04.890 --> 15:05.620
Over 20,000.

15:06.320 --> 15:07.870
Even if we raise that amount,
it's useless.

15:07.870 --> 15:08.380
Look.

15:10.100 --> 15:11.470
There goes the profit margin.

15:11.470 --> 15:12.070
The profit

15:12.080 --> 15:14.940
wouldn't even cover
our round-trip train tickets.

15:15.430 --> 15:16.340
He knows for sure

15:16.340 --> 15:18.030
we can't do without his batch.

15:18.510 --> 15:19.120
Ivan

15:19.150 --> 15:20.970
has done this before.

15:21.750 --> 15:22.640
Years ago,

15:22.670 --> 15:24.390
he took over several small businesses.

15:24.390 --> 15:25.480
Now he has the largest supply of hide

15:25.480 --> 15:26.750
in the whole market.

15:27.200 --> 15:28.270
Relying on this,

15:28.290 --> 15:30.690
he often jacks up prices
whenever he wants.

15:30.720 --> 15:32.620
This guy has connections,

15:32.790 --> 15:35.540
so nobody dares to cross him.

15:35.980 --> 15:38.410
His crew often smuggles contraband

15:38.430 --> 15:40.100
in their shipments.

15:40.620 --> 15:42.950
They've made a lot of money
over the years.

15:43.010 --> 15:44.210
Just last month,

15:44.240 --> 15:45.840
they made a large sum of money

15:46.340 --> 15:48.340
through my friend's freight depot.

16:16.030 --> 16:17.830
You didn't come with sincerity.

16:19.280 --> 16:21.340
Didn't we already give you the money?

16:22.040 --> 16:23.060
Yellow cowhide,

16:23.290 --> 16:25.100
$2.50 a piece,

16:25.370 --> 16:27.970
and buffalo hide, $2 a piece.

16:28.130 --> 16:28.890
Am I right?

16:35.150 --> 16:38.220
I said $10 and $6.

16:44.310 --> 16:46.620
You have a shipment heading to Shenyang.

16:47.580 --> 16:49.180
Here's the tracking number.

16:53.030 --> 16:55.150
What's in that batch of goods—

16:56.290 --> 16:57.690
will it pass inspection?

16:58.390 --> 16:59.070
My friend

16:59.960 --> 17:00.670
is at

17:00.670 --> 17:02.170
Russian customs right now.

17:02.170 --> 17:03.710
If I can't leave today,

17:03.960 --> 17:05.060
your shipment

17:05.380 --> 17:07.640
will receive some "special attention."

17:16.810 --> 17:18.310
You dare investigate me?

17:18.710 --> 17:19.530
No, no, no.

17:21.220 --> 17:22.950
I'm not the one investigating!

17:23.109 --> 17:24.890
Russian customs will be!

17:25.640 --> 17:28.380
If you honor the original prices,

17:28.980 --> 17:31.050
we'll put this whole thing behind us.

17:31.750 --> 17:33.240
Otherwise, we can just wait here

17:33.240 --> 17:34.420
and see who comes looking for you first—

17:34.420 --> 17:36.310
buyers

17:36.500 --> 17:38.160
or Russian customs officers.

17:47.460 --> 17:48.270
Frankly,

17:49.440 --> 17:51.170
we wouldn't be bold enough

17:51.280 --> 17:52.030
to do business out here

17:52.030 --> 17:53.890
without our connections in Russia.

17:53.890 --> 17:56.420
I'll come pick up the goods
tomorrow morning.

18:03.070 --> 18:04.820
Step aside. Let him go.

18:10.490 --> 18:11.690
Spasibo (thank you).

18:26.160 --> 18:27.220
Harasho! Harasho!

18:27.220 --> 18:28.040
Lower, lower, lower!

18:28.040 --> 18:28.920
Lower, lower!

18:29.610 --> 18:30.220
Lower it! Keep going!

18:30.220 --> 18:31.640
Over here! Come on, come on!

18:31.640 --> 18:32.220
Hold it steady.

18:32.220 --> 18:33.390
A bit more out, a bit more out!

18:33.390 --> 18:35.520
Good. Harasho! Lower it down!

18:46.720 --> 18:47.570
Careful.

18:47.740 --> 18:48.540
Wait a moment.

18:50.380 --> 18:52.190
Let's have a meal together.

18:53.570 --> 18:54.700
We'll skip the meal.

18:54.740 --> 18:57.000
We can just stick to business from now on.

19:13.750 --> 19:14.570
This time,

19:15.000 --> 19:16.000
we're definitely going to make big money.

19:15.050 --> 19:19.750
[Braised Noodles]

19:16.780 --> 19:17.330
Well, just come back

19:17.330 --> 19:18.030
and work with us.

19:18.030 --> 19:19.560
I was too hard on you before.

19:20.740 --> 19:22.710
I made myself clear that day too.

19:23.240 --> 19:23.850
There are

19:23.880 --> 19:25.310
two things in life that make me happiest.

19:25.310 --> 19:26.550
One is playing the saxophone.

19:26.550 --> 19:27.700
The other is...

19:28.610 --> 19:30.220
seeing my buddies

19:30.250 --> 19:31.450
doing better than me.

19:31.530 --> 19:32.790
I hope the two of you succeed!

19:32.790 --> 19:34.000
Alright then.

19:34.140 --> 19:35.400
Invest in us.

19:35.440 --> 19:36.660
When we make money, we'll split it.

19:36.660 --> 19:38.500
Doesn't that mean
I, your buddy, am doing well?

19:38.500 --> 19:39.440
I'm fine with a dividend share,

19:39.440 --> 19:40.520
but I can't invest—

19:40.550 --> 19:41.550
I've got no money.

19:41.920 --> 19:42.250
Then,

19:42.290 --> 19:43.010
just go borrow a bit from your mom.

19:43.010 --> 19:43.610
That's it.

19:43.770 --> 19:45.760
[Braised Noodles]

19:43.900 --> 19:45.400
Now you think of my mom.

19:45.550 --> 19:46.510
During the New Year,

19:46.510 --> 19:48.430
you rarely visited her!

19:48.460 --> 19:49.380
And we live so close.

19:49.380 --> 19:50.220
I was busy.

19:50.240 --> 19:50.920
During the New Year,

19:50.920 --> 19:51.940
I was in Russia, wasn't I?

19:51.940 --> 19:52.920
What should we do then?

19:52.920 --> 19:54.220
Besides, your mom is my mom.

19:54.220 --> 19:54.700
How about this?

19:54.700 --> 19:55.550
Okay, thank you.

19:55.550 --> 19:56.770
Let Mom invest.

19:56.980 --> 19:58.610
When we make money, we give Mom her share.

19:58.610 --> 20:00.010
Give Mom... Give Mom a...

20:00.510 --> 20:01.140
Xiaojun!

20:01.550 --> 20:02.080
Xiaojun!

20:03.410 --> 20:04.130
Mr. Duan!

20:06.240 --> 20:07.160
What a coincidence!

20:07.160 --> 20:08.180
What a coincidence!

20:08.180 --> 20:08.900
Where are you sitting?

20:08.900 --> 20:10.920
-How come I didn't see you earlier?
-I was in the private room.

20:10.920 --> 20:12.160
You're here to eat too?

20:12.160 --> 20:13.660
My buddy likes this place.

20:13.700 --> 20:15.010
No wonder I didn't see you earlier.

20:15.010 --> 20:16.680
Come on! Join us and have a drink!

20:16.680 --> 20:18.310
-I've already eaten.
-Sit! Let's eat together!

20:18.310 --> 20:18.900
I just finished.

20:18.900 --> 20:20.430
Well, let me introduce you.

20:20.750 --> 20:22.030
This is Shengli. Liangliang.

20:22.030 --> 20:23.570
-We're buddies doing business together.
-Nice to meet you.

20:23.570 --> 20:24.240
Nice to meet you, sir.

20:24.240 --> 20:25.170
This is Mr. Duan.

20:25.220 --> 20:26.310
Mr. Duan lent us the money

20:26.310 --> 20:27.310
for our business.

20:28.010 --> 20:29.420
Thank you, Mr. Duan!

20:29.500 --> 20:30.570
-Thank you!
-Mr. Duan!

20:30.570 --> 20:32.420
You really helped us in our hour of need!

20:32.420 --> 20:33.050
Never mind that.

20:33.050 --> 20:33.920
None of that formality.

20:33.920 --> 20:35.450
How's your business going?

20:35.570 --> 20:36.160
Well,

20:36.180 --> 20:37.090
we just finished stocking up the goods,

20:37.090 --> 20:38.090
and the three of us

20:38.160 --> 20:39.220
are having a little celebration here.

20:39.220 --> 20:39.850
Yes, yes.

20:40.010 --> 20:40.640
Mr. Duan, I'll say it straight—

20:40.640 --> 20:41.310
without you,

20:41.310 --> 20:42.440
we couldn't have started this business.

20:42.440 --> 20:43.270
Let me toast you!

20:43.270 --> 20:44.400
Come on, the three of us toast you!

20:44.400 --> 20:44.800
To you!

20:45.010 --> 20:45.790
-Use this cup!
-I'll pass on the alcohol.

20:45.790 --> 20:46.980
-Use this cup!
-I've already had quite a bit.

20:46.980 --> 20:48.260
Then I'll down one for you!

20:48.260 --> 20:48.640
No...

20:51.750 --> 20:52.410
Xiaojun!

20:52.500 --> 20:53.840
That's enough.

20:54.240 --> 20:55.100
Once your business is
properly up and running,

20:55.100 --> 20:56.010
we'll celebrate properly then.

20:56.010 --> 20:57.680
Okay, okay.

20:57.750 --> 20:58.880
Actually, Xiaojun,

20:58.880 --> 21:00.610
let me tell you the truth today.

21:00.720 --> 21:02.540
That money didn't come from me.

21:02.660 --> 21:04.000
It came from a good friend of mine.

21:04.000 --> 21:04.750
He specifically asked me

21:04.750 --> 21:05.950
to give you the money.

21:06.230 --> 21:07.170
We were actually having dinner together

21:07.170 --> 21:07.700
in a private room today.

21:07.700 --> 21:08.400
He just stepped out.

21:08.400 --> 21:09.260
By the way, Xiaojun,

21:09.260 --> 21:09.850
let me take you out

21:09.850 --> 21:10.770
to meet that friend.

21:10.770 --> 21:11.440
He's a really great guy.

21:11.440 --> 21:12.790
-Alright, alright, sure!
-Let's go.

21:12.790 --> 21:13.660
More friends, more opportunities, right?

21:13.660 --> 21:14.460
I'll go say hello first.

21:14.460 --> 21:15.340
Go ahead!

21:15.670 --> 21:16.840
Take care, Mr. Duan!

21:17.380 --> 21:18.240
Which one is he?

21:18.440 --> 21:19.460
You'll definitely need his help someday.

21:19.460 --> 21:20.510
Where did this Mr. Duan come from?

21:20.510 --> 21:21.900
He looks a bit unfamiliar.

21:21.900 --> 21:22.510
I don't know him either.

21:22.510 --> 21:23.290
I have no idea.

21:23.290 --> 21:24.720
He gave money to people
he's never even met?

21:24.720 --> 21:26.480
That's really something.

21:26.920 --> 21:28.250
That guy's car is something.

21:28.250 --> 21:29.450
What kind of car is it?

21:33.960 --> 21:35.220
Hello, sir. Thank you.

21:35.380 --> 21:36.240
Thank you, sir.

21:39.710 --> 21:41.830
[Seasons Change Hostel]

21:44.110 --> 21:45.480
[Seasons Change Hostel]

21:53.960 --> 21:54.680
Don't drink too much.

21:54.680 --> 21:55.290
-I'm heading off.
-Okay, okay.

21:55.290 --> 21:55.940
Okay, let's have a drink later.

21:55.940 --> 21:57.000
Alright, alright.

21:57.050 --> 21:57.750
Okay, okay.

21:57.880 --> 21:58.230
Bye.

21:58.440 --> 21:59.150
Bye.

22:02.140 --> 22:03.070
Come on, cheers.

22:05.030 --> 22:07.110
You should just invest the money.

22:07.180 --> 22:07.790
You don't have to do anything.

22:07.790 --> 22:08.660
Just sit back and wait for your share.

22:08.660 --> 22:09.290
I always thought

22:09.290 --> 22:10.570
it was Mr. Duan who lent us the money.

22:10.570 --> 22:11.670
It turns out to be that guy outside.

22:11.670 --> 22:13.470
That guy outside has real class.

22:13.700 --> 22:14.430
That guy said

22:14.540 --> 22:15.430
we don't even

22:15.720 --> 22:16.640
have to pay interest on this money.

22:16.640 --> 22:18.470
Wow, and he looks sharp too.

22:18.490 --> 22:19.550
Really decent guy.

22:20.490 --> 22:21.650
That guy is the real deal.

22:21.650 --> 22:22.270
Yeah.

22:23.320 --> 22:26.010
Ma Xiaojun. Come with me for a sec.

22:27.580 --> 22:28.140
What's going on?

22:28.140 --> 22:30.230
A few drinks and you call my full name?

22:31.590 --> 22:32.570
What's wrong,

22:33.570 --> 22:34.370
Young Master?

22:35.690 --> 22:37.040
They drove off and left!

22:38.290 --> 22:38.970
What?

22:39.340 --> 22:40.940
Never seen a nice car before?

22:41.090 --> 22:41.770
I'll borrow it someday

22:41.770 --> 22:43.130
and let you drive it.

22:43.270 --> 22:44.930
You jerk, Ma Xiaojun!

22:46.500 --> 22:47.720
Ma Xiaojun, have you no conscience?

22:47.720 --> 22:48.240
Do you know

22:48.240 --> 22:49.590
that was Chu Caiyuan's money?

22:49.590 --> 22:50.750
What Chu Caiyuan?

22:50.810 --> 22:52.280
You've had a few drinks
and lost your mind?

22:52.280 --> 22:53.930
How was I supposed to know
whose money it was?

22:53.930 --> 22:55.080
Are you crazy?

22:55.750 --> 22:57.160
Are you crazy?

22:58.140 --> 22:59.380
Let go of me!

22:59.830 --> 23:00.430
Screw you!

23:05.060 --> 23:05.860
Are you crazy?

23:06.060 --> 23:07.120
Are you crazy?

23:07.770 --> 23:08.900
You're insane!

23:09.660 --> 23:10.870
You drank too much!

23:10.940 --> 23:11.550
Jun!

23:15.840 --> 23:17.410
Ungrateful thing.

23:17.770 --> 23:18.850
You're not my friend anymore.

23:18.850 --> 23:19.670
Liangliang.

23:19.830 --> 23:20.900
Don't touch me!

23:23.220 --> 23:24.280
Don't be like this.

23:25.820 --> 23:27.080
You drank too much!

23:29.180 --> 23:30.580
You two do your business.

23:30.610 --> 23:32.330
You two go ahead
and do your business together!

23:32.330 --> 23:33.860
If you dare walk away today,

23:34.400 --> 23:36.110
we're done for good!

23:38.440 --> 23:39.370
Then we are done.

23:41.390 --> 23:43.050
I don't care if you drop dead out there!

23:43.050 --> 23:43.780
Liangliang!

23:49.710 --> 23:51.020
I really want to curse!

23:51.050 --> 23:51.980
Why didn't you

23:51.980 --> 23:53.500
tell me about this earlier?

23:53.500 --> 23:54.110
How was I supposed to know

23:54.110 --> 23:55.540
you borrowed the money from him?

23:55.540 --> 23:56.050
I've lived

23:56.050 --> 23:57.240
my whole life,

23:57.350 --> 23:58.270
and I've never once

23:58.270 --> 23:59.240
betrayed my buddy!

23:59.240 --> 24:00.420
What must Liangliang

24:00.420 --> 24:01.790
be thinking of me right now?

24:01.790 --> 24:02.850
Hurry up. Hurry...

24:03.550 --> 24:04.530
Wait, we spent all the money on the hides.

24:04.530 --> 24:05.260
Look at this.

24:09.330 --> 24:10.160
The first batch of goods

24:10.160 --> 24:11.090
is almost ready.

24:11.290 --> 24:12.700
We have to sell it quickly.

24:12.700 --> 24:13.330
Let's sell it quickly

24:13.330 --> 24:14.590
and pay the money back.

24:44.240 --> 24:45.170
Is it a good time?

24:45.860 --> 24:47.120
I'd like to talk to you.

24:47.530 --> 24:48.740
Let's go for a walk?

24:49.920 --> 24:50.960
Let's talk inside.

24:50.960 --> 24:52.160
I don't want to go out.

25:28.600 --> 25:29.130
Ranran,

25:30.700 --> 25:31.850
we've been acting awkward with each other

25:31.850 --> 25:32.950
for so long.

25:34.940 --> 25:36.380
Can you tell me what's wrong?

25:36.380 --> 25:38.180
I really can't stand it anymore.

25:40.380 --> 25:42.440
What have you been thinking about us?

25:43.030 --> 25:44.110
And if I did something wrong,

25:44.110 --> 25:44.980
just tell me.

25:45.010 --> 25:45.990
I can change.

25:47.310 --> 25:48.570
I really don't know...

25:49.720 --> 25:50.680
what happened between us.

25:50.680 --> 25:51.700
It's driving me crazy.

25:51.700 --> 25:52.960
Every day I lie in bed,

25:52.980 --> 25:54.270
I-I don't dare to close my eyes.

25:54.270 --> 25:55.140
As soon as I close them,

25:55.140 --> 25:55.850
I see you when you first came to

25:55.850 --> 25:57.280
the hostel.

25:58.200 --> 25:59.110
My mind is full of

25:59.110 --> 25:59.980
images of us.

26:02.680 --> 26:03.810
I want to sort it out.

26:04.880 --> 26:06.540
I know I can't.

26:10.530 --> 26:11.440
But I want to tell you

26:11.440 --> 26:12.770
that I haven't changed.

26:15.940 --> 26:18.000
My feelings for you haven't changed.

26:25.070 --> 26:26.000
I've changed.

26:27.310 --> 26:28.910
You haven't changed either.

26:29.000 --> 26:29.660
I have.

26:30.830 --> 26:31.560
You haven't.

26:31.850 --> 26:33.050
That's not an excuse.

26:36.580 --> 26:37.440
Liangliang...

26:42.330 --> 26:43.860
Let's just leave it at this.

26:45.940 --> 26:46.670
Let's end it.

26:53.640 --> 26:54.180
Why?

26:59.240 --> 27:00.710
There's no why.

27:06.460 --> 27:08.090
I did love you.

27:09.880 --> 27:12.140
A reckless, all-consuming kind of love.

27:14.460 --> 27:15.240
But you also know,

27:15.240 --> 27:16.500
when I came to Beijing,

27:17.510 --> 27:20.020
what I wanted to do most
was to be an actress.

27:20.690 --> 27:22.460
That's my biggest dream.

27:24.070 --> 27:25.800
I know you want to be an actress.

27:27.450 --> 27:28.980
And I never once thought about

27:28.980 --> 27:30.010
stopping you from being an actress

27:30.010 --> 27:30.830
or acting.

27:30.850 --> 27:32.500
I've always supported you.

27:34.070 --> 27:35.270
But the reality is

27:35.270 --> 27:36.600
that these two things

27:37.400 --> 27:38.680
have conflicted.

27:40.980 --> 27:43.250
These are two clearly

27:43.290 --> 27:44.780
separate paths.

27:49.480 --> 27:50.720
When both paths

27:50.740 --> 27:52.510
were laid in front of me...

27:55.310 --> 27:56.400
I made a choice.

28:00.830 --> 28:01.560
I thought...

28:03.570 --> 28:05.370
as long as you felt the same as me,

28:06.770 --> 28:09.200
I'd go down the same path with you
to the end.

28:14.020 --> 28:15.820
But you actually told me that...

28:18.380 --> 28:20.520
you weren't ready.

28:20.610 --> 28:21.550
It's not that I didn't want to

28:21.550 --> 28:22.660
or that I was afraid.

28:22.660 --> 28:24.190
I was just caught off guard.

28:24.500 --> 28:25.850
I never imagined

28:25.940 --> 28:27.340
my first time would be...

28:27.500 --> 28:28.350
like that.

28:28.370 --> 28:29.950
I never imagined this.

28:30.720 --> 28:31.640
I know.

28:32.680 --> 28:34.010
It wasn't your fault.

28:37.500 --> 28:39.360
But that was my first time as well.

28:45.440 --> 28:47.680
It's too late to talk about it now.

28:49.570 --> 28:50.850
You must have

28:50.880 --> 28:51.540
some idea of

28:51.570 --> 28:53.630
what happened between Mr. Chu and me.

28:54.610 --> 28:55.850
I don't want to keep going over this

28:55.850 --> 28:57.190
again and again.

28:58.290 --> 28:59.160
Don't force me

28:59.200 --> 29:01.160
to reopen my old wound again and again,

29:01.160 --> 29:01.680
okay?

29:03.960 --> 29:04.570
Ranran.

29:10.850 --> 29:12.240
It's all in the past.

29:12.830 --> 29:13.830
It's all over now.

29:14.440 --> 29:15.500
I can't get over it.

29:19.700 --> 29:21.560
I know I can't explain it clearly.

29:23.130 --> 29:25.460
But I've thought it through very clearly.

29:25.640 --> 29:27.050
I know what I want.

29:30.810 --> 29:32.010
I want to...

29:34.110 --> 29:36.640
I want to be with you—

29:37.010 --> 29:38.830
really be with you for a lifetime.

29:38.830 --> 29:39.740
I'll try my best

29:39.880 --> 29:41.680
to give you everything you want,

29:41.680 --> 29:42.640
everything you dream of.

29:42.640 --> 29:43.640
I'm pregnant.

29:58.590 --> 29:59.440
Just go.

30:06.940 --> 30:08.160
Whenever I see you,

30:09.900 --> 30:10.760
I can't help...

30:11.140 --> 30:13.220
I can't help thinking...

30:16.210 --> 30:18.310
if I had chosen

30:18.350 --> 30:19.920
another path back then...

30:23.640 --> 30:26.660
what would we be like now?

33:02.330 --> 33:02.830
Ranran!

33:04.290 --> 33:04.770
Ranran.

33:07.440 --> 33:08.570
Where are you going?

33:09.770 --> 33:10.600
I don't know.

33:11.810 --> 33:12.530
I was afraid

33:12.530 --> 33:14.170
you'd just up and leave without a word.

33:14.170 --> 33:15.900
You always say I'm like a child.

33:16.400 --> 33:18.130
Aren't you being childish too?

33:33.710 --> 33:34.970
Let's have a good talk.

33:37.830 --> 33:38.560
Liangliang.

33:41.480 --> 33:42.610
I have to leave here.

33:43.700 --> 33:44.570
If I stay,

33:46.640 --> 33:48.840
we'll only make each other suffer more.

33:50.380 --> 33:51.700
I can't face you.

33:53.570 --> 33:54.700
Don't push me, okay?

33:57.740 --> 33:59.600
The things you're telling me now—

34:00.830 --> 34:03.160
maybe I wouldn't have understood before.

34:04.250 --> 34:05.720
But now, I do.

34:07.050 --> 34:08.820
If none of this had happened,

34:09.340 --> 34:10.920
whatever vows I made to you,

34:11.840 --> 34:13.570
whatever feelings I declared—

34:14.880 --> 34:17.080
maybe it was all just heat of the moment.

34:17.760 --> 34:18.460
But I know

34:18.460 --> 34:20.790
that every word
I'm saying to you right now

34:20.840 --> 34:23.239
is something I've thought through deeply.

34:24.900 --> 34:27.159
I already missed my chance with you once.

34:27.230 --> 34:27.920
I don't want to

34:27.920 --> 34:29.150
miss it again.

34:32.190 --> 34:33.280
I don't want...

34:35.010 --> 34:36.380
our future...

34:40.030 --> 34:41.500
to be clouded by the past.

34:43.300 --> 34:44.080
You said

34:45.500 --> 34:47.070
you didn't know where to go

34:47.730 --> 34:48.760
or what your future life

34:48.760 --> 34:49.830
would be like.

34:51.530 --> 34:53.389
That's something I can't accept.

34:54.170 --> 34:55.650
If you leave now...

34:58.450 --> 34:59.670
and wander the world,

35:01.800 --> 35:03.380
I'll go find you right away.

35:04.420 --> 35:06.620
I'll search the ends of the earth for you

35:06.860 --> 35:08.350
until I find you.

35:08.530 --> 35:10.670
Then, I'll say everything
I'm telling you now,

35:10.670 --> 35:12.230
all over again.

35:14.650 --> 35:15.820
Instead of wasting time

35:15.820 --> 35:16.800
on that,

35:19.210 --> 35:21.180
why don't we use that time

35:22.760 --> 35:23.820
to love each other?

35:28.210 --> 35:29.070
Shen Ranran...

35:35.860 --> 35:36.330
I...

35:37.690 --> 35:39.090
I know I don't have much money now

35:39.090 --> 35:40.380
to buy you a ring.

35:41.780 --> 35:43.910
But the money I made going to Russia...

35:45.320 --> 35:46.170
with them—

35:49.760 --> 35:50.530
I used all of it

35:50.530 --> 35:52.260
to buy this little gift for you.

35:52.420 --> 35:53.170
I just never

35:53.170 --> 35:54.840
found the right moment.

36:00.210 --> 36:01.010
Just consider

36:01.940 --> 36:03.320
that I owe you a ring.

36:04.280 --> 36:06.410
I'll definitely buy one for you later.

36:06.460 --> 36:08.190
But today, I want to tell you...

36:10.420 --> 36:11.610
you can't leave me.

36:15.440 --> 36:17.400
My world—Tao Liangliang's world—

36:19.280 --> 36:20.810
means nothing without you.

36:25.090 --> 36:26.710
I'll definitely buy you...

36:27.230 --> 36:28.830
a ring you like in the future.

36:42.880 --> 36:43.740
Shen Ranran...

36:49.000 --> 36:50.930
I can accept everything about you.

36:55.630 --> 36:57.050
Will you be with me?

37:32.460 --> 37:34.500
I'll go back to Beijing
to check in with Director Weng.

37:34.500 --> 37:37.160
You go keep a close eye on
the factory in Wenzhou.

37:37.260 --> 37:38.860
You've found yourself such a

37:38.860 --> 37:39.880
good business setup.

37:39.880 --> 37:41.190
Zhuang Zhuang and your father-in-law

37:41.190 --> 37:42.280
are at the factory every day,
watching over things.

37:42.280 --> 37:42.670
They wish they could

37:42.670 --> 37:43.570
check every single stitch.

37:43.570 --> 37:44.170
Sometimes your father-in-law

37:44.170 --> 37:45.320
even does it himself.

37:45.320 --> 37:46.400
I was thinking
I could help you keep an eye on

37:46.400 --> 37:47.660
things here in Russia,

37:47.760 --> 37:48.530
and you could go back

37:48.530 --> 37:51.010
and spend more time
with your father-in-law.

37:51.010 --> 37:52.470
Let's talk about it later.

37:53.260 --> 37:55.260
With such a large volume of orders
right now,

37:55.260 --> 37:57.090
our product quality and production

37:57.090 --> 37:57.850
must keep up.

37:58.150 --> 37:59.010
Otherwise, all the effort

37:59.010 --> 37:59.780
Sophia spent opening the market for us

37:59.780 --> 38:00.710
would be wasted.

38:00.980 --> 38:01.670
My friends,

38:01.670 --> 38:02.700
let me tell you—

38:02.920 --> 38:03.730
these leather shoes

38:03.730 --> 38:05.880
have been incredibly popular here!

38:05.940 --> 38:07.760
I've compiled the sales figures.

38:07.760 --> 38:08.560
Take a look.

38:09.510 --> 38:10.730
Especially this one

38:10.820 --> 38:11.730
and this one.

38:11.840 --> 38:13.670
They've been selling particularly well!

38:13.670 --> 38:14.660
Is it possible

38:14.820 --> 38:16.050
that it's you who's popular?

38:16.050 --> 38:17.150
You're the reason

38:17.150 --> 38:17.980
we have

38:18.010 --> 38:19.210
a market here.

38:20.360 --> 38:20.870
No.

38:21.400 --> 38:23.800
They sell well
because of the good quality.

38:24.320 --> 38:24.770
Right.

38:24.920 --> 38:26.260
To tell you the truth,

38:26.320 --> 38:28.850
some shoes from Chinese factories

38:29.300 --> 38:30.760
were of very poor quality.

38:31.070 --> 38:33.470
They felt like
they were made of cardboard.

38:33.690 --> 38:35.090
They couldn't last a week

38:35.150 --> 38:37.030
and would fall apart once they got wet.

38:37.030 --> 38:37.900
Things like that

38:37.900 --> 38:40.230
damaged the reputation of Chinese goods.

38:40.530 --> 38:42.260
But our products are different.

38:42.260 --> 38:42.960
The quality is good,

38:42.960 --> 38:44.600
so everyone snaps them up.

38:45.420 --> 38:46.150
Sometimes I feel like

38:46.150 --> 38:47.750
I'm taking advantage of you.

38:48.070 --> 38:49.230
I haven't really contributed much

38:49.230 --> 38:50.460
to your business.

38:51.690 --> 38:53.970
What do you mean, "your business"?

38:54.070 --> 38:56.830
This is our business, right?

38:56.880 --> 38:57.820
Even though Xu and Zhuang Zhuang

38:57.820 --> 38:59.510
started it as a husband-and-wife shop,

38:59.510 --> 39:00.320
once the business grows,

39:00.320 --> 39:00.940
we could

39:00.940 --> 39:02.780
open an international division in Russia.

39:02.780 --> 39:03.510
Sounds good!

39:04.420 --> 39:05.420
Sounds good to me.

39:05.800 --> 39:07.730
See? An international division.

39:07.900 --> 39:09.150
An international division.

39:09.150 --> 39:11.630
[Guest Room]

39:15.280 --> 39:16.080
Can I help you?

39:18.020 --> 39:18.760
Could you tell me

39:18.760 --> 39:20.000
which room Shen Ranran is in?

39:20.000 --> 39:20.730
Who are you?

39:22.380 --> 39:23.260
I'm her friend.

39:23.650 --> 39:24.260
Wait.

39:24.500 --> 39:25.800
Does Ranran know you're coming?

39:25.800 --> 39:27.740
[Parking Area]

39:27.050 --> 39:27.710
Excuse me,

39:27.810 --> 39:28.860
I'll ask you one last time—

39:28.860 --> 39:30.090
which room is Shen Ranran staying in?

39:30.090 --> 39:30.960
Can you tell me or not?

39:30.960 --> 39:31.510
Well,

39:31.820 --> 39:33.340
j-just tell me

39:33.360 --> 39:34.110
what you want with her.

39:34.110 --> 39:34.600
None of your business.

39:34.600 --> 39:35.680
What do you mean, "none of my business"?

39:35.380 --> 39:38.540
[Parking Area]

39:35.710 --> 39:36.710
I'm the owner here.

39:36.710 --> 39:37.170
It is my business.

39:37.170 --> 39:37.960
Why are you getting physical?

39:37.960 --> 39:38.780
-None of your business.
-No!

39:38.780 --> 39:39.380
Wait!

39:39.530 --> 39:41.260
-What are you doing?
-Shen Ranran!

39:41.260 --> 39:42.190
What do you want?

39:42.320 --> 39:42.800
Let go of me!

39:42.800 --> 39:43.780
Shen Ranran!

39:43.840 --> 39:44.960
Why are you here?

39:47.240 --> 39:48.070
You again.

39:48.940 --> 39:49.820
I'm telling you—

39:49.820 --> 39:51.160
I must see Ranran today.

39:51.230 --> 39:51.760
No way.

39:52.500 --> 39:53.150
Get out of my way.

39:53.150 --> 39:53.760
No way.

39:54.920 --> 39:55.500
Listen up,

39:55.500 --> 39:56.760
I've had enough of you!

39:56.920 --> 39:58.020
Don't push it!

39:58.050 --> 39:59.380
Or I won't go easy on you!

39:59.400 --> 39:59.830
Step aside!

39:59.830 --> 40:01.150
You still can't go in!

40:01.280 --> 40:01.800
What?

40:02.650 --> 40:03.530
Asking for a beating, huh?

40:02.770 --> 40:07.380
[Guest Room]

40:03.760 --> 40:04.760
Stop right there!

40:05.000 --> 40:05.420
What are you doing?

40:05.420 --> 40:05.960
Let go!

40:06.480 --> 40:07.190
Let go of us!

40:07.460 --> 40:08.390
Help!

40:08.480 --> 40:09.780
They're hitting people!

40:09.780 --> 40:10.840
Haven't had enough beating?

40:10.840 --> 40:12.130
Haven't had enough?

40:15.860 --> 40:16.590
Let go of him!

40:16.800 --> 40:17.660
Let go of him!

40:18.420 --> 40:19.090
Bastard!

40:19.610 --> 40:21.030
Who told you to touch her?

40:21.230 --> 40:21.730
Boss!

40:22.380 --> 40:22.940
Ranran!

40:23.760 --> 40:24.530
What do you want?

40:24.530 --> 40:25.260
Let go of him!

40:25.380 --> 40:26.000
Let go!

40:30.110 --> 40:31.510
All of you, get back here!

40:43.960 --> 40:44.460
Ranran.

40:46.320 --> 40:47.050
Come with me.

40:48.030 --> 40:49.490
Let's find a place to talk.

40:51.650 --> 40:53.090
I'm not going with you.

40:54.610 --> 40:55.610
I quit acting.

40:56.500 --> 40:58.160
I have nothing to do with you!

40:58.590 --> 41:00.050
Even if you quit acting...

41:02.260 --> 41:03.660
we can still be together.

41:05.340 --> 41:06.540
I'm getting married.

41:09.320 --> 41:10.140
Back off!

41:16.710 --> 41:17.730
Are you sure

41:18.090 --> 41:19.590
the person you're marrying

41:19.590 --> 41:20.920
loves you more than I do?

41:27.210 --> 41:27.820
I am sure.

41:28.690 --> 41:29.230
Ranran.

41:30.340 --> 41:31.270
I was young once.

41:31.760 --> 41:32.230
I know

41:32.250 --> 41:34.250
"the world for two" that you imagine

41:34.940 --> 41:36.170
is not necessarily real.

41:36.170 --> 41:37.380
This world is big.

41:38.300 --> 41:40.260
This hostel is my world.

41:41.460 --> 41:42.630
Please leave.

41:48.070 --> 41:49.000
If my love for you

41:49.860 --> 41:50.500
has become

41:50.500 --> 41:51.700
a kind of harassment,

41:52.920 --> 41:53.570
I promise

41:54.730 --> 41:55.460
I will leave.

41:58.480 --> 42:00.050
But when you're out there alone,

42:00.050 --> 42:01.250
don't get bullied...

42:03.380 --> 42:04.440
and don't get hurt.

42:06.820 --> 42:08.280
If you ever really need me,

42:09.070 --> 42:09.920
give me a call.

42:13.630 --> 42:14.160
Goodbye.

42:16.280 --> 42:16.800
Sorry.

42:16.860 --> 42:17.300
Leave!

42:43.670 --> 42:44.800
-Ranran, you're bleeding!
-Are you alright?

42:44.800 --> 42:45.390
Ranran!

42:45.840 --> 42:46.500
What's wrong? What's wrong?

42:46.500 --> 42:48.860
Are you alright? Kid!

42:49.500 --> 42:51.090
Go call an ambulance!

42:52.130 --> 42:53.110
Kid!

42:53.230 --> 42:54.490
Are you alright, Ranran?
